	<h1 class="title">明星们都爱的这个设计师，为什么转行为残障人士做设计？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/194153/small/194153.jpg?1454682827" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">徐婧艾 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-03 18:14:35 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18437/medium/18437.jpeg?1449112974" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="18437" data-title="《明星们都爱的这个设计师，为什么转行为残障人士做设计？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/18437/medium/18437.jpeg?1449112974" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/18437.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
